<P>
   ISRAEL-TEACH (Jerusalem) _ The start of this school year marks a
quiet revolution in the teaching of Israeli history to most Israeli
pupils. New, officially approved textbooks make plain that many of
the most common Israeli beliefs are as much myth as fact. By Ethan
Bronner. 1,900 words.
