bathroom etiquette, arguments over who gets to watch what on
television. By Bill Pennington.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-DOLPHINS-JOHNSON (Davie, Fla.) _ Feature on Miami Dolphins
coach Jimmy Johnson. There are probably five coaches who could take
the sorriest team in football and by pure force of their will push
that franchise into the postseason. Johnson is one of them. Johnson
believes his Dolphins team is the most talented in the AFC East. He
may be right. With more weapons on offense than he has had since
joining Miami for the 1996 season, Johnson is poised to advance
deep into the playoffs. His Dolphins have a swagger, like Johnson's
old Dallas teams that won two Super Bowls. By Mike Freeman.
</P>
