<SLUG> BC-YELTSIN-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A RUSSIAN WHO'S STILL DANCING AS FAST AS HE CAN 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
