CONGRATULATIONS TO THE THOUSANDS OF CUSTOMERS OF MY FRIEND BILL
WILLIAMS' MANY FINE RESTAURANTS . . . UPON THE OPENING OF HIS
LATEST AND NEWEST IN HIS FABULOUS CHAIN . . . AND THE NEXT TIME
