<SLUG> BC-THISWEEK-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THIS WEEK IN REVIEW 
</HEADLINE>
  (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   `Rocky' and a Little Cannoli
</P>
<P>
   Most of the movies of Baltimore's open-air film festival are
available around the corner in the video shop for anyone who wants
to curl up alone for escape. So the likely reason for 800 people
gathering in the streets of Little Italy to watch the movies play
