<P>
   ``Ci vediamo al cinema!'' beams Ms. Cricchio. ``See you at the
movies!''
</P>
<P>
   _ By FRANCIS X. CLINES
</P>
<P>
   It Was Lead, Not Mercury
</P>
<P>
   People keep the strangest souvenirs. In 1815, an admirer of
Andrew Jackson was given a snippet of the great man's hair, and
those revered strands somehow survived to the present day. They
never blew away in a gust of wind, never got lost in the sock
