   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ATLANTA-CHINASIDE _ WASHINGTON _ Claude Calvin Collins of
Atlanta, 61, once a workaday computer consultant, says he ended up
becoming one of the Chinese government's ``go-to'' people in
America through Wang Jun, a well-connected member of the sons and
daughters of Communist revolutionaries who now run the country.
(Carr, Cox News Service). 21. MOVED.
</P>
