<P>
   OZ-KORY (Kansas City, Mo.) _ Robert Kory dreams of creating a
$771 million Wonderful World of Oz resort and theme park. But
skeptics point out that Kory, 50, is an entertainment lawyer who
has never built a theme park, that he is new to the theme park
industry and that Kory originally said the park would open in 1995.
The scheduled opening date is now 2002. By GRACE HOBSON. 3 takes.
Story will move in the ``a'' wire.
</P>
<P>
