Veterans of Foreign Wars national convention, don't expect to hear
war stories. The last thing heard when these veterans gather is any
talk of that particular hill, bunker or pillbox. The emphasis,
instead, is on love of country and humility. By BRIAN BURNES and
MATTHEW SCHOFIELD. Story will move in the ``a'' wire.
